sequenceDiagram
    participant AGENT as "arckit-datascout agent"
    participant MCP as "Data Commons MCP<br/>(datacommons-mcp)"
    participant API_GOV as "api.gov.uk"
    participant OUTPUT as "research/ARC-{PID}-DSCT-{NUM}.md"
    
    Note over AGENT: Step 6: Check MCP Availability
    AGENT->>MCP: Check if MCP configured
    
    alt MCP Server Available
        Note over AGENT,MCP: Statistical Data Validation Phase
        AGENT->>MCP: search_indicators<br/>(query: UK population, GDP, health, etc.)
        MCP-->>AGENT: indicator_ids + metadata<br/>(dcid, description, source)
        
        AGENT->>MCP: get_observations<br/>(indicator_ids, geo: UK/NUTS2 regions)
        MCP-->>AGENT: time-series data + quality metrics<br/>(coverage, granularity, update frequency)
        
        Note over AGENT: Validate Data Quality<br/>(completeness, timeliness, sub-national coverage)
        
        AGENT->>OUTPUT: Add Data Commons section<br/>(indicators found, quality assessment)
    else MCP Not Configured
        Note over AGENT: Skip Data Commons phase<br/>(proceed directly to UK Gov APIs)
    end
    
    Note over AGENT: Step 7: UK Government API Discovery
    AGENT->>API_GOV: WebFetch api.gov.uk<br/>(mandatory next step)
